    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An art review in Weekend on Friday about group shows at New York galleries referred incorrectly to a show at CRG in Chelsea that includes the work of Colby Bird, who has a sculpture in one of the group shows reviewed, ''In Defense of Ardor,'' at Bellwether in Chelsea. The show at CRG is a two-man show of work by Mr. Bird and Joshua Fields, not a solo show by Mr. Bird.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
